 Also in 2016, Shetty won the Business Excellence Award from the Indian Business & Professional Council.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nmchealth.com/news/dr-b-r-shetty-honoured-with-business-excellence-award/|title=Dr. B.R. Shetty honoured with Business Excellence Award|publisher=NMC Health|access-date=24 April 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170424085934/http://www.nmchealth.com/news/dr-b-r-shetty-honoured-with-business-excellence-award/|archive-date=24 April 2017|url-status = dead}}</ref> Middlesex University in Dubai awarded Shetty an Honorary Doctorate in 2016.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mdx.ac.ae/about-us/honorary-doctorates|title=Middlesex Dubai Honorary Graduates|publisher=Middlesex University Dubai|access-date=24 April 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170424174731/http://www.mdx.ac.ae/about-us/honorary-doctorates|archive-date=24 April 2017|url-status = live}}</ref>\n\nIn January 2017, Shetty was honored at the Annual Health Awards with a special award for his contribution to the region's healthcare industry.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://article.wn.com/view/2017/01/23/Dr_B_R_Shetty_honoured_at_the_Annual_Health_Awards_2017_NMC_/|title=Dr. B. R. Shetty honoured at the Annual Health Awards 2017 (NMC Health plc)|publisher=World News|access-date=24 April 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170424085508/https://article.wn.com/view/2017/01/23/Dr_B_R_Shetty_honoured_at_the_Annual_Health_Awards_2017_NMC_/|archive-date=24 April 2017|url-status = live}}</ref> The following month, Shetty received the Nadaprabhu Kempegowda International Award at the Kempegowda International Festival.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newskarnataka.com/nri/kempegowda-international-festival-lays-emphasis-on-uniting-okkaligas-under-roof|title=Kempegowda International Festival lays emphasis on uniting Okkaligas under roof|publisher=News Karnataka|access-date=24 April 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170424174146/http://www.newskarnataka.com/