0ab[[\u041f\u0440\u043e\u0432\u043e\u043a\u0430\u0446\u0438\u044f (\u0433\u0440\u0443\u043f\u043f\u0430)|\u041f\u0440\u043e\u0432\u043e\u043a\u0430\u0446\u0438\u044f]]\u00bb\n*\u00abPatron of Belarusian Culture\u00bb \u2014 \u00ab[[Amkodor]]\u00bb<ref>{{cite journal|author=\u041a\u043b\u0456\u043c\u0430\u045e|first=\u0410\u043b\u0435\u0433|last2=\u0421\u0430\u045e\u0447\u0430\u043d\u043a\u0430|first2=\u0410\u043b\u0456\u043d\u0430|date=2017-02-11|title=\u042f\u043d\u044b \u0430\u0431\u0443\u0434\u0436\u0430\u043b\u0456 \u00ab\u041b\u0456\u0440\u0443\u00bb|url=http://kimpress.by/?page=2&id=13870&mode=print|url-status=live|journal=[[Kultura (Belarusian newspaper)|Kultura]]|publisher=|volume=|issue=6 (1289)|pages=|issn=|archive-url=http://web.archive.org/web/20200411144608/http://kimpress.by/?page=2&id=13870&mode=print|archivedate=2020-04-11|accessdate=2020-04-11|via=|\u0441\u0442\u0430\u0440\u043e\u043d\u043a\u0456=|\u0442\u044b\u043f=|\u0433\u043e\u0434=}}</ref>.\n\n== Criticism ==\nAt the beginning of 2013, in his column over at [[Charter 97]], \u0179micier Padbiarezski of [[Radio Free Europe/Radio Liberty]] lamented that the organizers of the award in their nominations ''\u201cdo not notice''\u201d quite popular but partially censored artists in the country: [[Siarhei Mikhalok]], [[Lavon Volski]], [[Alexander Kullinkovich]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://charter97.org/be/news/2013/1/29/64569/|title=\u0417\u0431\u0440\u044d\u043d\u0434\u0437\u0456\u043b\u0456!|last=\u041f\u0430\u0434\u0431\u044f\u0440\u044d\u0437\u0441\u043a\u0456|first=\u0417\u043c\u0456\u0446\u0435\u0440|date=2013-01-29|authorlink=\u0179micier Padbiarezski|publisher=[[Charter 97]]|work=[[Radio Free Europe/Radio Liberty]]|language=be|url-status=live|archiveurl=http://web.archive.org/web/20200410201811/https://charter97.org/be/news/2013/1/29/64569/|archivedate=2020-04-10|accessdate=2020-04-10}}</ref>\n\nIn 2013, \u0179micier Biezkaravajny, founder of the music portal [[Experty.by]], noted that the award is ''\u201ca big project that is shown on television\u201d'' and ''\u201cfor winning in which people get money,\u201d'' while the critic questioned the quality of the composition of the jury on the example of the analysis of the II ceremony<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://euroradio.fm/bezkaravayny-galounae-razviccyo-adbyvaecca-u-mezhah-nezalezhnay-kultury|title=\u0411\u0435\u0437\u043a\u0430\u0440\u0430\u0432\u0430\u0439\u043d\u044b: \u0413\u0430\u043b\u043e\u045e\u043d\u0430\u0435 \u0440\u0430\u0437\u0432\u0456\u0446\u0446\u0451 \u0430\u0434\u0431\u044b\u0432\u0430\u0435\u0446\u0446\u0430 \u045e \u043c\u0435\u0436\u0430\u0445 \u043d\u0435\u0437\u0430\u043b\u0435\u0436\u043d\u0430\u0439 \u043a\u0443\u043b\u044c\u0442\u0443\u0440\u044b|last=\u041a\u0430\u043b\u0435\u0441\u043d\u0456\u043a\u0430\u0432\u0430|first=\u041c\u0430\u0448\u0430|date=2013-05-14|publisher=[[European Radio for Belarus]]|language=be|url-status=live|archiveurl=http://web.archive.org/web/20130815113325/http://euroradio.fm/bezkaravayny-galounae-razviccyo-adbyvaecca-u-mezhah-nezalezhnay-kultury|archivedate=2013-08-15|accessdate=2020-01-21}}</ref> what, coupled with other shortcomings, casts doubt on its national status.<ref name=\":1\" />\n\nHe also, at the request of Taras Tarralitsky of [[Belorusy i rynok]], confirmed the opinion of the interviewer that economic problems had reached the national stage with the cancellation of the ''\u201cdirective and artificial\u201d'' ceremony in 2015: ''\u201cIf there is an order, some designated channel conducts it. If there is no order, no one does. This is an indicator of the level of professional relationships within the pop community of Belarus, its spoiledness by state attention. Neither the professional community, as in many countries, nor the initiative group stand behind the award. [[Ministry of Culture of the Republic of Belarus|The Ministry of Culture]] should not get involved in such projects.\u201d''<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.belmarket.by/v-kulturnom-ostatke|title=\u0412 \u043a\u0443\u043b\u044c\u0442\u0443\u0440\u043d\u043e\u043c \u043e\u0441\u0442\u0430\u0442\u043a\u0435|first=\u0422\u0430\u0440\u0430\u0441|last=\u0422\u0430\u0440\u043d\u0430\u043b\u0438\u0446\u043a\u0438\u0439|website=|date=2015-12-28|publisher=[[Belorusy i rynok]]|language=ru|accessdate=2020-04-09|archiveurl=http://web.archive.org/web/20200409174057/http://www.belmarket.by/v-kulturnom-ostatke|archivedate=2020-04-09|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nIn a review of all music awards of Belarus for 2013, Pavel Sverdlov, editor of KYKY.ORG, described the second ceremony as an act that ''\u201cresembled the distribution of [[USSR State Prize|the USSR State Prizes]]\u201d'' but ''\u201cwith the difference that, no-no, representatives of the alternative scene slipped in among laureates though.\u201d''<ref name=\":1\">{{Cite web|url=https://kyky.org/music/pliaski-na-kostiakh-rok-karanatsyi-ili-zachiem-bielarusi-shiest-muzykalnykh-priemii|title=\u041f\u043b\u044f\u0441\u043a\u0438 \u043d\u0430 \u043a\u043e\u0441\u0442\u044f\u0445 \u00ab\u0420\u043e\u043a-\u043a\u0430\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0430\u0446\u044b\u0456\u00bb, \u0438\u043b\u0438 \u0437\u0430\u0447\u0435\u043c \u0411\u0435\u043b\u0430\u0440\u0443\u0441\u0438 \u0448\u0435\u0441\u0442\u044c \u043c\u0443\u0437\u044b\u043a\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u044b\u0445 \u043f\u0440\u0435\u043c\u0438\u0439|last=\u0421\u0432\u0435\u0440\u0434\u043b\u043e\u0432|first=\u041f\u0430\u0432\u0435\u043b|date=2013-01-31|website=|publisher=KYKY.ORG|language=ru|url-status=live|archiveurl=http://archive.vn/EXclY|archivedate=2020-03-21|accessdate=2020-03-21}}</ref>\n\n== \u041f\u0440\u0438\u043c\u0435\u0447\u0430\u043d\u0438\u044f ==\n{{\u043f\u0440\u0438\u043c\u0435\u0447\u0430\u043d\u0438\u044f|2}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{cite web|author=|title=\u0423\u043b\u0430\u0434\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u0456\u043a\u0456 \u041d\u0430\u0446\u044b\u044f\u043d\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u0430\u0439 \u043c\u0443\u0437\u044b\u0447\u043d\u04